    "section_text_8MUdPj": {
      "type": "section-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_hLX8Dc": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>WANDERINGS™ </em>Collection: <strong>PEONIES</strong></p>",
            "size": 60,
            "margin_bottom": 50,
            "heading_highlight_type": "highlight-color",
            "highlight_color": "#000000",
            "highlight_text_color": ""
          }
        },
        "text_TAJynC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With thousands of peonies photographed over a decade, our Signature Limited Edition WANDERINGS™ PEONIES Collection showcases the peony in all her glory — from bud to bloom to later stages of life.</p>",
            "size": 100,
            "max_width": 575,
            "margin_bottom": 25
          }
        },
        "text_XrhBnt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The WANDERINGS™ PEONIES Collection pushes boundaries, to celebrate each flower’s entire lifecycle, illuminating the delicate balance between life and decay. It captures the bloom and the fall, as colors and forms shift, and new perspectives emerge. In doing so, it reflects upon the circle of life, and challenges a society obsessed with perfection.</p>",
            "size": 100,
            "max_width": 675,
            "margin_bottom": 25
          }
        },
        "text_gxC6p8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Within the photographic process, what ultimately emerged was a ‘light’ glowing from within each flower—no matter how much it looked ready to be forgotten. It was both poetic and profound. Each flower had something to say—at every stage of life.</p>",
            "size": 100,
            "max_width": 675,
            "margin_bottom": 25
          }
        },
        "separator_8jCiMT": {
          "type": "separator",
          "settings": {
            "separator_width": 30,
            "margin_top": 50,
            "margin_bottom": 50
          }
        },
        "text_KHGkie": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Due to the large body of work, the WANDERINGS™ PEONIES Collection is presented in 15 approachable Parts. Like the flowers themselves, each Part of this PEONIES Collection is made up of many artworks and series that both stand alone, as well as unfold chronologically as a cohesive body of work. Forming a continuous narrative when experienced together, the entire Collection follows hundreds of flowers’ journeys.</p>",
            "size": 100,
            "max_width": 700,
            "margin_bottom": 25
          }
        },
        "text_LtQKFx": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Not all available artwork is featured on this website. If you would like to see the full WANDERINGS™ PEONIES Collection, please email us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@shopwander.com\" title=\"mailto:hello@shopwander.com\">hello@shopwander.com</a> to get access to our WANDERINGS™ Catalogs, which contain the entire Collections, in full.</p>",
            "size": 100,
            "max_width": 1000,
            "margin_bottom": 25
          }
        }
      },
